"
A network is made up of at least two devices that connect and communicate via a wired or wireless connection. 
One network switch can connect to another switch to link two networks.
Not only can two network switches be connected, 
but multiple ones can be connected to form an interconnected network like the internet.
"


Data Center Servers
Web Servers: Website Hosting, Databases, CMS Software, Control Panel, Email
Web Requests: Device <---> Web Server <---> Website



"
A server is a computer that runs applications and services, ranging from websites to instant messaging. 
You have just learned about a web server which is a specific type of server.

Web servers can handle thousands of requests from clients per second.     
Web servers have to be able to handle high volumes of web requests.

A web server can function as website storage and administration.     
Web servers have multiple functions and this is just two of them. 
They can also handle security and manage emails.

A web server can handle security.     
Web servers have multiple functions and this is just one of them. 
They can also function as website storage and administration and manage emails.
"


